name: Magner's Fingers
description: "Pimp Blue Rikki" by The Disco Biscuits was played at The Fox theater in Boulder, CO, January 31, 2010.  I shot a lot of shaky video for fun at the show, and then felt compelled to animate this when I was learning rotoscoping and After Effects compositing. Song can be heard here: https://archive.org/details/db2010-01-31.dpa4027.flac16/db2010-01-31dpa4027d2t02.flac#
